          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "NymVPN runs a background service (daemon) \u2028to keep your connection secure. It handles encryption and routing, protecting your activity even when the app is closed.\n\nFollow the steps below to install the daemon."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "NymVPN runs a background service (daemon) \u2028to keep your connection secure. It handles encryption and routing, protecting your activity even when the app is closed.\n\nFollow the steps below to install the daemon."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "NymVPN runs a background service (daemon) \u2028to keep your connection secure. It handles encryption and routing, protecting your activity even when the app is closed.\n\nFollow the steps below to install the daemon."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "NymVPN, bağlantınızı güvenli tutmak için arka planda bir hizmet (daemon) kullanır. Daemon, uygulama açık olmasa bile şifreleme ve yönlendirmeyi yönetir, böylece çevrimiçi etkinliğiniz her zaman korunur.\n\nDaemon ile ilgili yükleme adımlarını izleyin."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "NymVPN використовує фонову службу (daemon), щоб захистити ваше з'єднання.\n\nDaemon обробляє шифрування та маршрутизацію мережі, навіть коли програма не відкрита, тому ваша онлайн-активність залишається захищеною в будь-який час.\n\nПісля реєстрації та авторизації daemon запускається автоматично."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "NymVPN runs a background service (daemon) \u2028to keep your connection secure. It handles encryption and routing, protecting your activity even when the app is closed.\n\nFollow the steps below to install the daemon."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "NymVPN runs a background service (daemon) \u2028to keep your connection secure. It handles encryption and routing, protecting your activity even when the app is closed.\n\nFollow the steps below to install the daemon."
          }
        }
      }
    },
